    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People concerned with the preservation, improvement, and restoration of the natural environment, as well as the policies and politics associated with environmental preservation. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
